explanations;reload: Reload is measured from when reticle disappears to when it comes back. Not all weapons had a reticle. Timing may be off by up to 0.1s.
explanations;startingMagsDisclaimer: Starting mags for support weapons are currently unmeasured, but become max after the ship module upgrade.
explanations;laserFire: Laser weapons can't actually set things on fire. The data may be there to make the corpses burn.
